data.description: SPACE, SPACE, SPACE!! Don't get lost downstairs! This 4 bedroom 1.5 bathroom offers tons of space for you to do just about anything. A extra room for storage or home office. New carpet, updated flooring, stainless steel appliances, new paint, floored basement, Close to shopping and so much more! Seller is offering $4,000 towards your closing cost , schedule your showing today.
